**Javascript Solutions:**

*Javascript: Top-Down TLE without Memo*
```
let minDistance = (A, B) => {
    let go = (A, B, i, j) => {
        if (!i || !j)
            return i + j; // 🛑 base case: we have exhausted A or B, return "leftover" distance
        return Math.min(
            go(A, B, i - 1, j - 1) + Number(A[i - 1] != B[j - 1]), // ✅ match xor ❌ mismatch
            go(A, B, i - 1, j) + 1, // ❌ insertion
            go(A, B, i, j - 1) + 1  // ❌ deletion
        );
    };
    return go(A, B, A.length, B.length);
};
```

*Javascript: Top-Down with Memo*
