        //a^b = a^(b%6) (mod 7) = a1 (mod 7), because a^6 = 1 (mod 7) when a cannot divide 7, when a can divide 7, a1 is always 0
        //a^b = a^(b%190) (mod 191) =a2 (mod 191)
