# Intuition of this Problem:
We can solve this problem using various methods:
- Trie data strucutre
- dynamic programming

But I solved this problem using simple recursion - dfs.
![WhatsApp Image 2023-01-27 at 7.35.18 AM.jpeg](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/d47869df-216b-4184-a650-00035a86e96c_1674785146.2162044.jpeg)


