Hum approach mein ye kar rahe hai ki prefix and suffix ko check karenge ki agar current word ka prefix and suffix hamare set mein hai toh usse apne answer mein rakh lo ya phir agar prefix set mein hai and suffix ek concatenated word hai toh usse bhi check karlo and agar uska answer bhi true milega toh apne answer mein rakh lo usse.
